reviewText: This tape portrays juvenile delinquency in America beginning in the early 1940's.  There is a scene with J.Edger Hoover asked about the rise in juvenile delinquency.  The tape is hosted by Mamie Van Doren at the very beginning.  The tape shows scenes from popular '50's 'teenploitation films.

Teenage Confidential is a compilation film of juvenile delinquents, and rock and roll. It even has Tab Hunter giving a PA for mental health ! Hosted by the Fabulous Mamie Van Doren. I have met Mamie and she is so nice to her fans. I admire her for her stand on women's and gay rights. A living legend, and one of the last stars of the Golden Age of Hollywood.
